These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding, handball, sailing, baseball, basketball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Sport   | rugby | sailing | baseball | skateboarding | handball | cycling | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: lilac, brown, blood-red, chestnut, pink, aquamarine, turquise
1. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Color   | lilac | pink | blood-red | aquamarine | chestnut | brown | turquise |

