2. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Birthday   | november | june | february | may | march | july | august |

